==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Ј''', '''ј''' (''italics: Ј, ј'')

#The eleventh letter of the Serbian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is ''ј'' (j) and it corresponds to the English '''y''', as in '''y'''ou''. It is preceded by [[и|И]] and followed by [[к|К]]. It is sometimes considered as an equivalent of the Russian [[й|Й]].

